{"article_id":"UKg39ya6PgGXjALd","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Trump will land in Las Vegas on Wednesday","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"to console a city","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"- and a nation -","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"still reeling from the deadliest shooting spree in modern U.S. history .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"Caught between the latest gruesome images","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"highlighting the nation ' s epidemic of gun deaths","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"and a GOP-led U.S. Congress","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"that has been moving to roll back restrictions on firearms ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Trump is likely to offer sympathy to the victims","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"- but not propose any changes to gun laws .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"In the wake of the attack on a country music concert","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"that claimed 59 lives","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"and injured more than 500 people ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"Trump has carefully avoided any discussion","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"of how U.S. policy might be changed","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"to address a gun violence problem","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"that is by far the worst in the developed world .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"The U.S. has more than five times the per capita rate of gun homicides as Canada and more than 10 times that of the Netherlands and France .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"Pressed by reporters on whether the bloodshed in Las Vegas would prompt him to take up gun-control legislation ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Trump on Tuesday demurred","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"and instead praised first responders and volunteers","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"who worked","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"to save lives .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"\" Look , we have a tragedy , ''","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Trump said Tuesday .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"`` What happened is , in many ways , a miracle .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"The police department , they ' ve done such an incredible job .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"And we ' ll be talking about gun laws","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"as time goes on . ''","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Trump :","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"Las Vegas shooting suspect is ' a sick man , a demented man '","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"Congress faces paralysis on guns in wake of Las Vegas shooting spree","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"The three gun debate bills","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"to pay attention to in Congress","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"According to a White House statement about the trip ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"Trump is going \" to offer his support to those","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"recovering from their wounds ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"and to thank the courageous first responders . \"","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"What ' s unclear is whether Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"who has a penchant for unscripted remarks ,","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"will repeat comments","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"he 's made","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"after other gun massacres .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Trump has previously said","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"that more guns would have helped stave off further violence .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"He called for people to carry more guns","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"after shootings in Orlando in 2016 and several times in 2015 after tragedies in Paris and San Bernardino , Calif .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"FBI statistics show a recent uptick in gun violence","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"as mass shootings appear to be increasingly deadly .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"The death toll after a 2012 school shooting in Newtown , Conn. , was 26 .","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"In an Orlando nightclub in 2016 , 49 people were killed .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"Polls show broad public support","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"for extending criminal background checks to all gun purchases ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"including Internet sales .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"According to a June 2016 Quinnipiac University poll ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"93 % support this change .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"Another 6 in 10 support renewing the expired ban on assault weapons ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"the survey found .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"From a political perspective , however , there appears to be little appetite","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"for changing these laws .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"Trump has declared himself a strong Second Amendment supporter","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"and has already reversed an Obama-era ban on gun ownership by people","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"ruled mentally `` defective '' by the Social Security system .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"The National Rifle Association ,","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"with a number of gun industry representatives","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"serving on its board of directors ,","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"was among Trump 's earliest corporate backers .","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"\" You came through big for me ,","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"and I am going to come through for you , \"","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"he said at the NRA ' s April convention in Atlanta .","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"Both White House press secretary Sarah Sanders and Trump have said","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"now is not the time","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"to discuss policy .","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"And ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"as he gaveled in the Senate floor Tuesday ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"Majority Leader Mitch McConnell , R-Ky. , extended his thoughts and prayers to the Las Vegas shooting victims","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"before promptly pivoting to taxes .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"Trump has significantly changed his position on access to guns over time .","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"In a 2000 book ,","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"he said","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"Republicans \" refuse even limited restrictions , \"","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"they \" walk the NRA line. \"","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"He expressed support for the assault weapons ban and longer waiting periods","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"to purchase guns .","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"More than a decade later , Trump began to argue","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"that gun background checks \" accomplished very little \"","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"and declared himself \" a very big Second Amendment person. \"","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"In a 2015 interview on MSNBC 's Morning Joe , Trump said","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"mass shootings are a fact of life .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"In early 2016 , Trump said","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"the gun issue is a matter of states ' rights .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"`` It is a state issue","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"and we can certainly help , ''","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"Trump told a news channel in Grand Rapids , Mich .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"Even so , he allowed that something is amiss .","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"`` I remember 30 years ago","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"I just do not remember","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"these things happening , ''","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"Trump said then .","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":201,"left":0,"right":200,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":200,"left":118,"right":199,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":104,"right":117,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":1,"right":103,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":102,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":109,"right":116,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":107,"right":108,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"